Ingress rules.

USAGE:
  scw vpc ingress-rule <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  create      Create an ingress rule
  delete      Delete an ingress rule
  get         Get an ingress rule
  list        List ingress rules
  update      Update an ingress rule

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for ingress-rule
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -B, --beta             Enable beta mode
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw vpc ingress-rule [command] --help" for more information about a command.
